{"tid":1430461,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警方應優先處理迪士尼","createTime":"2019-08-07T17:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T18:13:38.000Z","uid":161551,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7552ebcac568c863cdaa57b12957205f31bba632","tid":1430461,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:53:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Hi 我又借Account啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌任屌<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><strong>呢篇野真係心曲 麻煩睇清楚先</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n作為一個愛國愛港既新中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />青年，我可以證明點解偉<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">你老母</span>大既香港警察要掃蕩迪士尼<br />\n<br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">售賣攻擊性武器</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mGBC21M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmGBC21M.jpg&h=da41db70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B03m9TqAzx1/?igshid=e6ykj9vjopmq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB03m9TqAzx1%2F%3Figshid%3De6ykj9vjopmq&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJcIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=ca0db5e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB03m9TqAzx1%2F%3Figshid%3De6ykj9vjopmq&h=77e79bf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B03m9TqAzx1/?igshid=e6ykj9vjopmq</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一個係激光劍 一個係激光槍</span></span><br />\n同樣都係來自Star Wars既外星勢力<br />\n<blockquote>外星勢力名單（部分）：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><ins>-加密中-</ins></span><br />\nLeia<br />\nHan Solo<br />\nChewbacca<br />\nR2D2<br />\nBB8<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><ins>-加密失敗-</ins></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><ins>-<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>資料已洩漏-</strong></span></ins></span><br />\n</blockquote><span style=\"font-size: large;\">深水埗賣激光槍</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而迪士尼竟然光明正大咁賣激光劍俾暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n唔怪得之已經咁多學生暴徒啦<br />\n原來全部都<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去晒迪士尼入貨</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">恐怖份子</span></span>既形象<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做玩具賣俾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RAsOqio.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRAsOqio.png&h=78b92ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個恐怖份子最擅長既就係激光槍<br />\n迪士尼既然講呢個恐怖份子整左做玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知頭唔知路既小朋友買左咪大獲？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">耳濡目染啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">迪士尼霸佔香港土地空間</span></span><br />\n迪士尼面積<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">0.35平方公里</span></span><br />\n而<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港既陸地面積只有1106平方公里</span></span><br />\n除返開之後 我地可以見到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">迪士尼用左0.03%既香港土地啊</span></span><br />\n西九龍站淨係用左0.11平方公里<br />\n咁即係迪士尼搞到香港起少左3個鳩鐵站啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知中國對我地幾好㗎起少3個高鐵站<br />\n即係話香港既旅客人次應該係宜家既4倍啊<br />\n用8月內地訪港旅行團數目計下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><del>0x4=0</del></span></strong></span><br />\n如果每人平均消費666蚊<br />\n起少3個高鐵站咪好肆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知的<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果不是中国 你们早就死了</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">吸納外國特工 安插係鬧市入面</span></span><br />\n有人同我講過 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">迪士尼其實有好多外籍員工</span></span><br />\n好多都住係旺角嗰頭<br />\n其實嗰班係美國政府派既間諜黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次示威遊行見到既外國人其實都係間諜<br />\n拎住電話拍片就係要回報情況俾美國中情局<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">有個外國人摸一摸塊面然後R褲係手勢黎<br />\n要示威者去 錫。警。察。春。袋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾恐怖啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n5.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同超能力組織同埋軍火商有合作</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B0Jek3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB0Jek3A.jpg&h=d24bcea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左邊係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">美國首富兼最大軍火商老細Tony Stark既發電廠同埋基地</span></span><br />\n而右邊既係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">神盾局仲起緊既基地</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢兩樣野都係係迪士尼入面<br />\n你話幾恐怖</span>？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以話 唔該警察快點執柒左呢間咁恐怖既野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"c6ca9b865f55de2717c3e5cfb97873e5620c547e","tid":1430461,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"464b9302905b5936ae21044b0044e02cc58b4990","tid":1430461,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d568d2fdfeccd642ad32ac80d0a6fef9ac561b","tid":1430461,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fa9645a2a9cd670d7c70f1bb5aca30cd264cbd","tid":1430461,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:54:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4baf6d9856188a6a735879cfcf71751feec0069","tid":1430461,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515f21c2ca27dd8df75d2ca11eed6395c652980d","tid":1430461,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f442d1a159dc2b33d7c5d5ccb74209c10e44d0","tid":1430461,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b605291eb760ebe2e2af898bb83f50de83f7df","tid":1430461,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff432df5125efcc0bee5637d9d4cfa838edbb44c","tid":1430461,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:55:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1c53bbdd26c24e7258a0f40bfc2a39d987c7ea","tid":1430461,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61522de3cd7750ad9f748a55daa3eddaf0412375","tid":1430461,"uid":161551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:56:38.000Z","msg":"成功十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1faa706efbed1f928516a47da9efc928bdbfdf94","tid":1430461,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:58:18.000Z","msg":"幫手推啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309fc477eb29c842ba216577de2b81eaa27a87ec","tid":1430461,"uid":161551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bZq4JnK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZq4JnK.gif&h=2c98c9a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d59c761c302d6b21cf17d74391a859c228bcf47b","tid":1430461,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}